<paragraph blockId="3.[174,1233,175,266]" pageId="3" pageNumber="20">
N o t e. The only representative of the genus in 
<collectingCountry box="[768,867,175,201]" name="Ukraine" pageId="3" pageNumber="20">Ukraine</collectingCountry>
. In 
<collectingCountry box="[909,1066,175,201]" name="United Kingdom" pageId="3" pageNumber="20">Great Britain</collectingCountry>
