<bibRefCitation author="Ball, S. G. &amp; Morris, R. K. A." pageId="3" pageNumber="20" pagination="1 - 130" refId="ref5646" refString="Ball, S. G. &amp; Morris, R. K. A. 2014. A review of the scarce and threatened flies of Great Britain. Part 6: Syrphidae. Species status, No. 9, Joint Nature Conservation Committee, Peterborough, 1 - 130." type="book chapter" year="2014">Ball &amp; Morris, 2014</bibRefCitation>
).
</paragraph>
